{"arkId":"cl010100745","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010100745","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1585 - 1600","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1585,"endYear":1600,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Noytoulon, Christophe","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1589","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1607","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10049","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale ; bo\u00eetier muni de deux couvercles mont\u00e9s \u00e0 charni\u00e8re. Pourtour orn\u00e9 d\u0027une frise. Couvercle du cadran figurant parmi les rinceaux fleuris Ponce Pilate se lavant les mains : le gouverneur assis tourne la t\u00eate vers deux conseillers, tenant ses mains au-dessus d\u0027un bassin tendu par un serviteur agenouill\u00e9. Couvercle du fond pareillement orn\u00e9 de rinceaux montrant le gouverneur debout aupr\u00e8s du Christ et d\u0027un soldat, l\u0027arrestation se d\u00e9roulant sous les yeux d\u0027un gar\u00e7on et d\u0027un vieillard. Carrure d\u00e9cor\u00e9e d\u0027une frise compos\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris ponctu\u00e9s de dauphins et de chim\u00e8res. A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur des valves, guirlandes de feuillage grav\u00e9es ; pendant d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de fleurs ; bouton moulur\u00e9. Cadran \u00e0 double cercle d\u0027heures (I \u00e0 XII et 13 \u00e0 24) ; au centre, vue de village avec un paysan tenant un b\u00e2ton ; autour, un mascaron, un vase, des t\u00eates d\u0027oiseaux. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et coqueret grav\u00e9s et ajour\u00e9s de rinceaux.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : NOYTOULON","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,5","displayDimension":"6,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,3","displayDimension":"3,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,2","displayDimension":"2,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Lyon (Rh\u00f4ne-Alpes = Rh\u00f4ne Alpes-\u003ERh\u00f4ne)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), vente \u00e0 Paris Drouot, 18-23 d\u00e9cembre 1916, n\u00b0 131 ; collection Claudius C\u00f4te (1881-1956), Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date 